fields.name: Bio Pet Active – Shampoo For Dogs With Aloe Vera 400ml
fields.description:
With its Aloe Vera extract and other ingredients, it nourishes the skin and coat of dogs with sensitive skin, giving them more strength and shine.
Its pH-balanced formulation and effective moisturizing properties keep skin moist and prevent dryness.

fields.name: Bio Pet Active Natural Honey Shampoo for Dogs, 400ml
fields.description:
Its pH balanced formulation and effective moisturizing property keeps the skin moist and prevents dryness.
It is a care shampoo for dense furred dogs, to make it easier for wet and dry fur brushing.
Its honey essence, imparts extra shine and softness by nourishing the skin and fur.
Natural Honey Shampoo for Dogs
